original_font_information.description: Futura is the ultimate geometric sans serif typeface family originally designed by Paul Renner and produced by the Bauer Type Foundry in Germany. The Bitstream version (Futura BT) is very popular because of its faithful interpretation of this classic design. Functional, yet friendly with one foot in the past and another toward the future, Futura has stood the test of time. This new version of Futura BT features an expanded character set with wider support for European languages.
